{"tid":1958828,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發 台灣有隻game因為中國武漢肺炎被取消代理。","createTime":"2020-04-05T03:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T05:38:53.000Z","uid":238660,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d977300d340fdef52e3e4670b9bf734498fffee1","tid":1958828,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/05/112933_7ef8b764c269495e02eaa3bd93135f14.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F05%2F112933_7ef8b764c269495e02eaa3bd93135f14.png&h=c532d9c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/05/112935_228f5f4169f1c5871fba8fdfa3b50bdb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F05%2F112935_228f5f4169f1c5871fba8fdfa3b50bdb.png&h=ad5b6a31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/05/112935_07de5c31ef81fcc96e6492f9f41fc47b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F05%2F112935_07de5c31ef81fcc96e6492f9f41fc47b.jpeg&h=fa14dda1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/05/112936_d52145d29ad39a419e100fb94e0a9caa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F05%2F112936_d52145d29ad39a419e100fb94e0a9caa.png&h=4a0f76de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國宣布為了要對新型冠狀病毒疾病（武漢肺炎）疫情鬥爭犧牲的同胞進行深切哀悼昨（4）日舉行了全國性哀悼活動，中國發行的遊戲多半宣布關閉伺服器已表示哀戚，更有台版遊戲跟進暫停服務，如《碧藍航線》、《閃耀暖暖》、《崩壞 3rd》等知名遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n而在台灣由網銀國際代理的《劍俠情緣叁》一早宣布進行臨時停機維護，全體頻道包含密語世界陣營好友幫會通通實施禁言，有玩家在遊戲中提及疫情相關的話題，被中國網友截圖後向原廠檢舉，導致越來越多人遭到封鎖，也使得玩家抱怨連連。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對此，遊戲原廠西山居遊戲深夜發布微博，表示 4 月 4 日當天有使用者惡意發表有關疫情的不當言論，因此在第一時間勒令台服代理運營商立即整改，更說「舉國為抗擊新冠肺炎鬥爭中的犧牲烈士和逝世同胞哀悼之時」對該舉表示譴責，更進一步說：「在大義面前，底線不容觸碰！西山居對此必將嚴肅處理！」、「願逝者安息，願生者奮發，願祖國昌盛。」貼文底下中國網友讚聲一片，甚至表示應該關服，更說服裝造型代理比較便宜，不差台灣玩家的收入等。<br />\n<br />\n對此，今（5）日凌晨網銀國際發布聲明表示堅持維護台灣玩家的發話權益，公告中提到：「原廠如果堅持要規範不合台灣既有的言論環境，我們將不惜終止合約，停止與中國廠商的任何商務合作。」隨即，西山居遊戲也發布聲明表示正式終止合作。<br />\n<br />\n網銀國際發布聲明表示堅持維護台灣玩家的發話權益<br />\n突如其來的決定讓台灣玩家相當錯愕但也備感欣慰，紛紛大讚網銀國際「沒有跪」真的是太好了，畢竟遊戲能代理，言論自由可是不行的啊！"},{"pid":"9e360d044a8be1b7aa7e7dbf2b29f87c0704701f","tid":1958828,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695f764c458df17e6d469ccf9688ec97a76764ae","tid":1958828,"uid":238660,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:32:07.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母 死赤匪"},{"pid":"01d4a6dc06fbd9565b9a0c29a368c4bffc684796","tid":1958828,"uid":278587,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ETTdv2oUYAAVq8k?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" />"},{"pid":"de438fc62ef50d81d978d94c7207295f38a82bdd","tid":1958828,"uid":238660,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:38:28.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bP3kBO6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbP3kBO6.png&h=849e740a&s={SIZE}\" />..<br />\n<br />\n劍俠情緣參-中華民國，香港，澳門服-網銀國際有限公司代理於2020年4月5日死於中國武漢肺炎 #RIP"},{"pid":"d8d25ac820e7d1be667b058d78bce185eb0ed347","tid":1958828,"uid":33418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:49:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />赤匪"},{"pid":"434bb40deafab94b1a3cb3c1d83d0ee5244f348f","tid":1958828,"uid":259674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:50:08.000Z","msg":"聽到未聽過"},{"pid":"d3c16836efc34244055cc3f2f35d2a09467237f6","tid":1958828,"uid":6845,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:51:28.000Z","msg":"呢間代理正 唔跪 出邊有post 有詳情"},{"pid":"243c7bb12ff8ca6fdaa90232d6f3cfb363d33f04","tid":1958828,"uid":43413,"like":